      • Transaction

        public Transaction​(int fromAccountID,
                   int toAccountID,
                   int fromUserID,
                   float amount,
                   TransactionType transactionType,
                   java.sql.Date transactionDate,
                   java.lang.String transactionDescription,
                   TransactionCategory transactionCategory)
        * creates new transaction * Takes from to which account money should be transfered if from or toAccount does not exist in database it is seen as external transfer and money goes or comes from default account
        Parameters:
        fromAccountID - defines account from which transaction is outgoing
        toAccountID - defines account from which transaction is going to
        fromUserID - defines user from which transaction is outgoing
        amount - amount of money to be transfered
        transactionType - type of transaction
        transactionDate - date of transaction
        transactionDescription - description of transaction
        transactionCategory - category of transaction
